A state of sliding instance
===========================
When energy within you are not under smooth control of you then it automatically create waves within your mind/heart with support of senses or imagination and when the waves get
created on surface of mind or surface of heart it automatically get transmitted from you mind/heart to the surrounding where you engage.

If your smooth and reliable understanding create the waves in under your awareness then you are able to look the transmission of waves and the waves are under control of your understanding/observation, since you have created the waves in under light state, it not automatically get transmitted beyond you but your observation send the waves in surrounding,
There is a purpose of creating the waves and that purpose is nothing but to knowing the structure/dimension/frequency/ behavior of waves and  this things gating detected by the observers not by mind. 
Normally mind either get flow with energy transmission or it fight with transmitted energy where as observation be with its flow, it never try to touch with purpose of fight of flow.

This is for the purpose to understand the states of energy gating changed at each and every moment of their transmission.
Here observation just looking actively the changing the states of energy and their direction of transmission.

But when the waves get created in you mind/heart without your awareness then this waves automatically get transmitted from your surface of mind/surface of heart, if you try to stop (what normally it do)then it create the stress/heart since it is nature of waves/energy to transmit after its creation, it can't be stop, you many control it smoothly but it will never come
in control forcefully.  Controlling of energy/waves can be possible  till a certain threshold for smooth transmission but stopping the waves always break the boundary. You get stress
or happiness to stop the energy is one thing but nature never go beyond its fundamental principle, it flow/stream simply towards its stability.

The purpose of waves gating created in your mind/heart is same as the purpose of waves created by observation the difference is only one is beyond the awareness and later is
within the observation/awareness.
In both state the waves try to stabilize it states. you looking/observing the same  or flow with it or you fight with is
is different things and it depends up on the energy within but transmission of energy is beyond your steps of activity, it can affect at certain level of threshold but not forever.

Due to under control the waves the observation gating experience since it purpose to just look the states of waves but when the waves are beyond your control your wishes come in picture to control forcefully and your energy of wishes get frighted with the transmission of energy.

***It is the unawareness/lack of understanding who makes you slide in world***

