your mind get they try this energy for its existence strongly. It collect the dust of energy for its own purpose. This types of energy haven't enough intensity to drill/touch the inner energy.
 
This is nothing but sliding the instance in outer world ie the world of mask/the world of object/the world of lust/the world of greed/the world of expectation/the world of hell/the world of stress/the world of poor understanding/the world of complexity/the wold of relativity..so on.
The above examples are not the example of world but these are the example of states of mind
 
